{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"a3cd7632-ce63-47a4-96c9-7177abaea81c","content":"No files found in the working directory. I'll provide the solution directly.\n\n## Converting to Compiled Bindings\n\nAdd `x:DataType` to your `ContentPage` to enable compiled bindings:\n\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" ?>\n<ContentPage xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n             xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n             xmlns:vm=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.ViewModels\"\n             x:Class=\"YourApp.Views.SettingsPage\"\n             x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\">\n\n    <VerticalStackLayout Padding=\"20\" Spacing=\"15\">\n\n        <Entry Text=\"{Binding Theme}\"\n               Placeholder=\"Theme\" />\n\n        <Switch IsToggled=\"{Binding NotificationsEnabled}\" />\n\n        <Stepper Value=\"{Binding FontSize}\"\n                 Minimum=\"8\" Maximum=\"48\" Increment=\"1\" />\n\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding FontSize, StringFormat='Font Size: {0}'}\" />\n\n    </VerticalStackLayout>\n</ContentPage>\n```\n\n**Key change:** The `x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"` attribute tells the XAML compiler to resolve all `{Binding ...}` expressions against that type at compile time.\n\n## Catching Binding Errors at Build Time\n\nAdd this to your `.csproj`:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n    <!-- Treat binding failures as build errors -->\n    <MauiStrictXamlCompilation>true</MauiStrictXamlCompilation>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\nWith compiled bindings enabled (`x:DataType`), misspelled or non-existent properties (e.g., `{Binding Themee}`) will produce **compile-time errors** rather than silent runtime failures.\n\n**Tips:**\n- If you need to opt out for a subtree (e.g., dynamic context), use `x:DataType=\"x:Null\"`.\n- Compiled bindings also improve performance by avoiding runtime reflection.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"887b7210-274e-4019-900c-e4029fb1c47e","outputTokens":505,"requestId":"A85F:25F1DB:623601:71F7E4:69FBE226"},"id":"52eed75d-5389-405e-9b31-59c1afbbbf14","timestamp":"2026-05-07T00:52:00.477Z","parentId":"804b65d7-9cbf-49cd-adc0-eafeb75be826"}
